            <title>[MNG-3498] StringIndexOutOfBounds -1 during path translation while reading pom.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-3498</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;directory&amp;gt;${basedir}&amp;lt;/directory&amp;gt; expresses this. The problem is that the DefaultPathTranslator expects there to be more than the simple basedir expression, and chokes if it encounters that expression as the only part of the value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
